title: 4 Secrets To Becoming a Role Model
dc:creator: Tracy Brinkmann | Personal Development in the spirit of Tony Robbins, Napoleon Hill, & Zig Ziglar
description:
Have you ever wondered exactly what traits you need to be considered a role model that has a positive effect on others? A Role Model that they look up to? The role model whose behavior they emulate? How can you be a positive influence? Is it something you have to actively do? Or is it based on your natural make-up? Some say role models are born, but it is also very possible to develop the traits and skills of a good role model. I have the quick helpful guide to becoming the role model you desire and to reach Your Success At Last! - CLICK & LISTEN then LIKE & SHARE!

Your Success At Last DNA | Personal Development in the Spirit of Tony Robbins, Napoleon Hill, Robert Kiyosaki, Jillian Michaels, Jack Canfield, Brian Tracy, Jim Rohn and Zig Ziglar

Think Successfully & Take Action!Tracy "Ace" Brinkmannhttp://YourSuccessAtLast.com
